    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I think it would be wise if my right hon. and gallant Friend left it to me to describe my opinion.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-83d2d154-6cf2-4b80-aea1-c6079a798ae8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-03-16/debates/2c7a5836-6c4e-4e02-b3c6-3693afa03db9/CivilAviation#contribution-83d2d154-6cf2-4b80-aea1-c6079a798ae8">
